<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="https://igu1.ucanapply.com/images/webicon.png" type="image/png">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Syllabus Management - IGU Meerpur</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/index.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f7f6;
        }

        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .success-message {
            color: green;
            background-color: #e8f5e9;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, filter 0.2s ease;
        }

        button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            filter: brightness(1.1);
        }

        button:active {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .btn-create { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #218838 100%); box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.3); }
        .btn-edit { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #17a2b8 0%, #117a8b 100%); box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(23, 162, 184, 0.3); }
        .btn-print { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6f42c1 0%, #563d7c 100%); box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(111, 66, 193, 0.3); }
        .btn-admin { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007bff 0%, #0056b3 100%); box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.3); }
        .btn-account { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffc107 0%, #e0a800 100%); color: #000 !important; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.3); }
        .btn-logout { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc3545 0%, #c82333 100%); box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.3); }

        .button-group {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px 15px 5px 15px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .group-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #6c757d;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .action-row {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        .action-row button {
            margin-bottom: 0;
            flex: 1;
            font-size: 14px;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        .dashboard-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .rules-container {
            background: #fff8e1;
            border: 1px solid #ffeeba;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 30px;
            max-width: 550px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #856404;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        @media (min-width: 1024px) {
            .dashboard-wrapper {
                flex-direction: row;
                align-items: flex-start;
                justify-content: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="dashboard-wrapper">
    <div class="container">
        <img src="https://d2xe8shibzpjog.cloudfront.net/logo/igu_logo.png" alt="IGU" style="height: 80px; width: auto;margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <h1>Syllabus & Course Management</h1>
        <p style="color: #555; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: bold;"><%= locals.message || "" %></p>
        <% if (locals.query && locals.query.message) { %>
            <div class="success-message"><%= locals.query.message %></div>
        <% } %>
        
        <div class="button-group">
            <div class="group-title">Program Management</div>
            <button class="btn-create" onclick="window.location.href='/program-specialization-form'">✨ New Program/Specialization</button>
            <button class="btn-edit" onclick="window.location.href='/programs-list'">✏️ Edit Program/Specialization</button>
        </div>

        <div class="button-group">
            <div class="group-title">Course Management</div>
            <button class="btn-create" onclick="window.location.href='/courses'">➕ Create New University Pool Course</button>
            <button class="btn-edit" onclick="window.location.href='/courses-list'">📚 View, Edit, or Download Courses</button>
        </div>

        <div class="button-group" style="margin-bottom: 25px;">
            <div class="group-title">Document Generation</div>
            <button class="btn-print" onclick="window.location.href='/generate-full-syllabus'">🖨️ Generate Full Syllabus Print Document</button>
        </div>
        
        <div class="action-row">
            <% if (locals.role) { %>
                <button class="btn-admin" onclick="window.location.href='/register'">👤 Register Admin</button>
            <% } %>
            <button class="btn-account" onclick="window.location.href='/editPass'">🔑 Edit Password</button>
            <button class="btn-logout" onclick="window.location.href='/logout'">🚪 Logout</button>
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="rules-container">
            <h3 style="margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 18px; color: #856404; border-bottom: 1px solid #ffeeba; padding-bottom: 10px;">📋 Workflow & Rules Guide</h3>
            <ol style="padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 0; line-height: 1.6;">
                <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><strong>Step 1 (Admin):</strong> Create a new Program with or without a Specialization.<br>
                    <span style="font-size: 13px; color: #666;">👉 Click <strong>"New Program/Specialization"</strong> (<code>/program-specialization-form</code>)</span>
                </li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><strong>Step 2 (Admin):</strong> Define Program Details & Mapping Parameters (POs/PEOs).<br>
                    <span style="font-size: 13px; color: #666;">👉 Click <strong>"Generate Full Syllabus Print Document"</strong> ➔ <strong>"Fill Details & View"</strong> (<code>/generate-full-syllabus</code> ➔ <code>/program-details-form</code>)</span>
                </li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><strong>Step 3 (Admin):</strong> Build the Curriculum Framework and assign Credit Schemes.<br>
                    <span style="font-size: 13px; color: #666;">👉 Click <strong>"Edit Program/Specialization"</strong> ➔ <strong>"Edit"</strong>. Assigning a Code & Scheme automatically generates empty "shell" courses!</span>
                </li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><strong>Step 4 (Teachers/Admins):</strong> Fill out Course Data or create Pool Courses.<br>
                    <span style="font-size: 13px; color: #666;">👉 To Edit Shells: Click <strong>"View, Edit, or Download Existing Course Syllabi"</strong> ➔ <strong>"Edit"</strong>.<br>
                    👉 To Create Pool Courses: Click <strong>"Create a New University Pool Course"</strong> to build global electives from scratch.</span>
                </li>
                <li><strong>Step 5 (Admin):</strong> Generate the Final Syllabus Document.<br>
                    <span style="font-size: 13px; color: #666;">👉 Click <strong>"Generate Full Syllabus Print Document"</strong> ➔ <strong>"Fill Details & View"</strong> ➔ <strong>"Save Details & Generate Syllabus"</strong></span><br>
                    <strong style="color: #d9534f;">Rule:</strong> The entire curriculum and all its courses must be fully completed before printing is permitted.
                </li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>